    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Solid project or budget driver with a strong-running engine, responsive automatic transmission, and a chassis that still feels planted on the road. Not a show car, but it has the kind of honest, usable character enthusiasts appreciate: dependable start-up, good low-end pull, and the bones of a well-engineered platform. Ideal for someone wanting affordable transportation, a weekend fixer, or a base for light restoration. Priced to move and worth a look if you want real mechanical potential without spending big.",
